      <title>美联储降息后加密货币与美国股票的关联度接近纪录高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/crypto-s-correlation-with-us-stocks-nears-record-in-fed-fallout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据相关性研究，数字资产和美国股票的走势比过去任何时候都更加同步，这表明推动股市的宏观经济变量也在影响加密货币市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/crypto-s-correlation-with-us-stocks-nears-record-in-fed-fallout</guid>
